Additionally, the paper may also fall under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) as these fields often involve multiclass classification problems and may benefit from the proposed algorithm.
